values:
i wish i could evict people from my dreams.
the level of disgust i have is only surpassed by our current economic defecit.
why?
why?
why?
because some times cunts just happen. 

my ego helps me out alot. 
i know i'm the best, i know i will always soar high above, i just wish i never looked at you.

first off, dramatha, gurl fran, i need to find you on facebook. i miss talking to you on here, but i don't get on here as often and i'd like to keep in touch.

I moved from Dallas to Wichita Falls. I'm living here with my gf.
not at all what i thought it would be, but life never really is.
waiting sooooo long for my dental assisting certificate to come in has me real down. Not working just really depresses me.

there's alot going on that i don't even know how to write about. i hardly ever write anymore, maybe that's what's going on with me lol.

my life isn't horrible, or bad, or anything of the sort. But i don't know how to handle this reality. this life. i've never felt some vulnerable. so on the edge. i've never been so dependent, and i hate it. 

my father is about to go to prison, and my gf wants to fuck other people...monogamy is such a funny thing i suppose. i wish i could find it.

i'm having a hard time establishing guide lines, rules, etc of what is and what is not acceptable within a relationship.  for some reason we just can't seem to get on the same page. i don't really know what's happening. i'm writing it off as an adjustment period, and my gf being young and out of control. i really do love her. if i didn't, god knows i'd be gone.

life is going.
responsibility is not something i love, but who does?

i miss the old me some times, but i feel a lot better now.

i do still want to get off of my meds some times and just write.  so much has happened, so much has changed. but it isn't bad at all. that's not what i'm saying.

this isn't as popular as it once was, but to the few that do still read, i actually want to get married. it's a mind blowing thing for me some times still.

i hate how medication does kind of kill my soul. but this world kills me without it, so not writing is the lesser of the two evils. 


I'm a certified dental assistant now, i'm trying to try. i haven't made it by my own standards yet, but i'll settle for the low bar society throws up there until i can climb a little higher.

i'm going to have time to be more creative from time to time now. i'm out of school for a while. but this holiday season is busy. i despise the bussle of the holidays. i'd be so much easier if we weren't such a transient society at times. but i love to travel.

i haven't typed on a actual key board in a while, just my blackberry. so i have been typing a "z" along with every "."   haha, it's fucking me up.

the world is a good place today.

i have written.   meds, and no longer being an angsty teen cuts back on creativity


You took my hand so easily
Did you not feel the Devil behind me?
I wrapped my arms around your neck and held you tight
It was easier to slip on your noose
The love you thought was illuminating your soul
Was my mouth setting you on fire
The embers of words burn you beautifully
when i kiss my lips to yours i can smell smoke
how i can go for hours is no mistake
your numbness is no coincidental
i'm slowly taking you apart
it's much easier to sell the pieces back to you
you are such a beautiful mess
my mouth waters with the anticipation of dragging you down
my foot will break your fall
along with the pieces of your self respect
broken dreams shine so bright on your scars of self loathing
looks like you've been busy
don't worry my angel
i'll bare the burden of that load for you
you can scream his name all you want
no one can hear you
just you, and me
when your veins run dry
is when you will be free
the ground is the only destination for those running from themselves
i'm glad you signed up
my smile sealed the deal
now, put your seat in the upright position
lock your tray table
i have no intentions of you returning
i've already sold tickets for the show
it's easier to watch someone else be torn to pieces
than to look in a mirror.


i wrote that a few days ago, and changed it alot from the page to here, they never feel finished...


in other news, i just want to be kissed. oh my god, i miss the taste of your mouth...i wonder if i'll get to be there again? who knows what this life holds. i just miss having you (by "have" i meant having sex)

Is an odd thing.
it's a growing beast really.
it requires alot of feeding.
and once you awaken it, it is a full time job
but if that time ever comes
just know, 

i will singe the hairs on my arm in order to throw you into the fire.

sitting in stagnate conversations wondering will this circle ever end..? 
i want to vomit.

i cannot say that today has been any more...well i don't know what more it could have been.

i'm not in a bad state, nor is anything wrong.

but at least once a day, i find myself saying " i feel soo unusual today, so weird."  but if it's a daily occurance then i suppose it isn't that unusual now is it? ha ha. 
i had a thought bubble, but it floated off. 
i'm not the same person i once was.
but i can't forget. i don't exactly want to remember everything either though. 
is this real?
will this moment even be remembered tomorrow...most likely not.

that's alright though. not everything is meant to be epic.
but there isn't much adventure in the mundane.

today, is just different.
i can't seem to see the forest for the trees.

maybe one day i'll have this figured out, but not today.

come on in, i've got to tell you what a state i'm in.

it's beautiful.   right now is one of those introspective moments.
i'm here (obviously) at the computer. I'm listening to "warning sign" by cold play.
i listen to the melody, let the electronic stream flow through my mind while i look to my left and see the most beautiful thing i've ever laid eyes on. and i love her

Tomorrow i go to my eldest little brothers graduation.
Back to Kentucky for a few days.
That place is just weird now.
But it is okay in small doses.
I miss my family.
But i don't like it there, and my dad doesn't like me.

last time i went up there it was a good trip. even though it was b/c my grandpa died. I hope this one will be good too. i'll ty my hardest.

it's hazy, and i love this song today. it's gives me a sufficient amount of get up and go. the right amount to return to counting inventory.  i am going to respark my land here. i need an outlet from the sort of domestication i am in i suppose.  ti's not really domestication, just trying to exist in the "real world" it's not a blast.

today was just kind of shitty
so what if i don't meet friends in a way you consider "normal"   FUCK YOU
i need a hobby
i need money for a hobby
i am so fucking pissed off at the world toda, and everything in it.
at the stars above, and the dirt below. everythign down to the air that flows
through my lungs
what a riot my mother begun
when she let me live


fuck this day.
i'm not you, and you aren't me. people just do things differently.
i wish you would get the fuck off of my back about it.

not everyone can be a somebody, i mean after all, we have t have someone to hold our spotlights for us whlie we walk out the door and greet the world



a close friend of mine is going through a bit of drug problems. this came into my head, but i can't finish. i was talking to her through this process, and i had to stop and puke.

what a world
with a sky riddled of grays and various browns
isn't the end of your world so tragically beautiful?
If you had it all back again
you would still piss it all away
Same shit, Different day.
There is no heart left in you to break
No more blood to let
When you opened your veins to ease your pain 
all of the good left

Christmas time...not to sound like a scroog, but i am ready for it to be over.
i am ready for some moments of silence.
not a sound.

"Maybe the United States can Divert 10% of the money on wars to fight aids in Africa?"

i was searching for the names of all 40 of the african countries. coincidently enough i came upon a website statistics. numbers of HIV/AIDS, oil consumption, natural gas consumption, etc.  and at the bottom of the community it had a forum with the above question as the subject.    needless to say it kind of got to me on a personal level. i can not speak for the military, nor on behalf of it.  but i have friends that get deployed everyday. almost everyone that gets deployed on this base goes through our office. we have to do their dental clearances. the point being ( i got off topic) people, young, very young people are over ther fight, and dieing with inadequate armor and weaponry as is. my friend jason had to take kevlar off of his dead fellow coreman and put it on himself to stay protected under enemy fire. the military in general is going through a process that has left us crucial in #'s. we can't afford to lose anymore. i'm not saying i agree with the course of action that has been taken. but i will support my fellow armed forces members where ever that may be.  
Definition of a Veteran

	A Veteran - whether active duty, retired, national guard or reserve - is someone who, at one point in his life, wrote a blank check made payable to "The United States of America", for an amount of "up to and including my life."
	
	That is honor, and there are way too many people 

	in this country who no longer understand it.
	
	-- Author Unknown
this is all the truth i have to give. and i will give it all.

i have been highly irritable as well as saddened lately.
i'm fearful for my mother, and my nana. the two women that raised me aren't doing so well. and i can't be beside them through it. i'm thinking about being medicated again. i've never really been a praying kind of girl, but now it's the only thing i can do.

get better mom, you can get through this.
nana, be careful, i'm sorry i can't be there to take care of you.

1. Do you remember how we hooked up through LJ? 
       i believe it was through a community but i am not for certain which one for certain, my, i am bad friend.

2. Do you have any new ink from a traditional Japanese artist yet? 
        yes i do, i have a pic of it on my myspace. i hae a lotus sititng in water and the outline of a womens hand pulling petals off of it. the petals flow down about a 5 inch scattered area. and each one has words on it. the phrase is "pull the petals off of you to make you tell the truth" it starts at myshoulder bone and goes to about 2 inches above my elbow. it's my favorite, and only color piece i have.

          when i was 10 we had this old blue truck. the floor board was almost rusted through entirely. but my dad would take us out to the river (my brothers and i) and he'd let me drive until we got to our swim spot. those were some of the best times i ever had.

i don't know what i want to do today. i believe i will leave work and sleep. i feel like more, but i want to ignore the world at the moment.

last night i dreamed sad dreams.
but this one was highly symbolic.
it was a medley of emotionally pulling instances.
it started out being back home.
we were walking down the main holler (my family and i) and we were logging out the road by the creek side.
i fell in the creek and there was a large deer there. my dad picked me up though.  we continued on about our job. then we walked home.
the next scene was me and sam partying at rachels house. which of course doesn't fly anymore (rachel said she couldn't hang with me b/c i'm too  "wild")
we were having me a going away trip b/c i was leaving to go to europe. but we were flying out of louisania b/c i was leaving my car with my mother in louisania.
there's this cruise i was going to go on before i went to europe. boarding occured in this mall in louisania. so i dropped my mom off, and began my vacation. i had this very long escalator ride in order to board. i was holding onto the handle and my feet wouldn't touch. but it was imparitive to hold on b/c this escelator went sideways and almost upside down. just as i thought i was going to fall the escelator stairs turned into a chute, and i was able to slide down into the ship. as soon as my stomach sets foward on the ship a man greets me and tells me my room is 419 (that's my room here) so that was funny to me.  i get to my room and it has two queen beds. one of which is already occupied. not a big deal, but it was taken by jade.  wow...apparently i made god mad at me for something...that's what i was thinking in my head. what kind of fucked up joke. was i there to just lay i nmy bed while her and her bf are there fucking?  it was weird.  made me think alot. i hate that.

wow.
it amazes me how one can warp such an instance.
and carry on about it in such a cold manner.
a week and a half ago i was i na very minor wreck with a woman.
since i don't drive and it wasn't my car i have no insurance.
i agreed to pay the damages on the ladys car.
we agreed on small payments at a certain garage.
behind my back she e-mails my commanders saying that i have made no contact and such and how she wants all of my wages to be garnished in order ot pay for her car to be fixed.
this is ridicelous.
i'm hating life at the moment.

hello all, long time no talk
i live in japan now.
it's crazy awesome.
i'll be here for two years, then it's back state side
or i might try to push for somewhere in europe.



just dreaming of you

had some thought
my head is clear
it's time to retreat a bit within myself
it's time to not speak
time for me to grow up
and realize all i need is me
so now i prepare the dreadful goodbye to you
b/c i know that i'll always want to be there
i'm a million miles away
but my heart, eyes, arms, and ears are right there
i know what happens in my absence
i know what's going on
as meaningless as it may seem
i know better
i've never been dumb
i just always chose the paths of self destruction.
i can't help it
i love what isn't the best thing for me
some how or another i suppose i'm subconsciously self destructive
you clean yourself up and make yourself presentable
but it just fucks you over
maybe it's the fact that i can feel it though
maybe it's the revival of the spirit that attracts me to such set sirens.
who knows.
either way i am slowly realizing that you are nothing more than a figment of the inner depths of my heart.
and it's time for me to wake up.

going to be a dental asst.
wow.  school isn't exactly a fucking piece of cake, but i manage.
the dorms are bad ass.

this place has an over whelming sense of isolation.
i miss someone sooo fucking much.
it sucks
being here
with no one that you know
in esence we are all seperated from everyone here.
it's nto bad, dont' get me wrong, just the feeling sucks, not the place.

i go to japan. i'm excited as hell but at the sametime i want it ot be over with so i can pursue something else. i'm kind of jumbled, but then again i'm not. my thoughts are jumbled, not me. i miss just doing nothing sometimes. i miss talking until all hours of the night.

peace out fucker bitches,
Amber G.

i now have a car. and i drove the hell out of it yesterday.

first trip: Tomball to sheri's to visit O. well that's a few miles needless to say.

2nd trip: danielle, kiara, alee, & i going from the apartments to southside, which is the hood close to pearland, and back.

3rd trip: danielle, kiara, and i going back to southside to pick up leah.

4th trip: taking leah back to southside this morning. 

all in all roughly 300 miles. and i LOVE it. last night was fucking kick ass. some guys got the crap beat out of them buy the cops in front of us. it was a bit funny, b/c they were some dumb motherfuckers. trying to evaid(sp?) arrest. dumb asses. 

going out for a job on monday with kiara after we drop danielle off. i miss those girls. 

lots of orange juice was drank last night. orange juice so owns.

teens are going to be kids, can't expect them to be serious.

life is deep, but good. i fucking love it. it's kicking my ass and i love it.

i'm not quite ready for august 8th. but i'm getting there.

i sit here and listen to this song and i can't help but get flooded by memories of you. "hate metoday, hate me tomorrow. hate me for all the things i never did to you." once again blue october is talking to me. everything about it relates to me and you and the days when we were whatever it was that we were. something beautifully fucked up. and it's nto that i miss what it was. i mean the friendship is even more than i could've hoped for really.  we aren't albe to fit it all inot one song, but this is the closest i've heard yet. i want to make an album to chronolog our epicjourney. one that isn'tyet over.  no...not that crazy stalker like way guys. one as in i know that we will continue to keep in touch and talk.b/c we have that bond. yeah we fuck eachother up sometimes, andthrow eachother off. but when it comes down to it we're there for eachother. and that issomethingyou just don't find now a days...haha rememberno sex means no false rape claims, that one cracked us up for a while. ahah still does really. eating tacobell and looking atthe stars. some badass times, ones that i will never forget, b/c even though we have a fucked up bond,it's a strong one none theless, and one i cherish. you're my best friend...ever.
you know i got to give it to trent, nothing really places a log of self loathing in you like he does...nothing.
